{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSTokensRaw\/documentation\/OUDSTokensRaw","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensRaw\/documentation\/OUDSTokensRaw\/GridRawTokens"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:13OUDSTokensRaw04GridB6TokensO22gridExtraCompactMarginSdvpZ","roleHeading":"Type Property","title":"gridExtraCompactMargin","extendedModule":"OUDSTokensRaw","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"gridExtraCompactMargin"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"GridRawToken","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:13OUDSTokensRaw04GridB5Tokena"}],"modules":[{"name":"OUDSTokensRaw"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudstokensraw\/gridrawtokens\/gridextracompactmargin"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"static"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"gridExtraCompactMargin","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GridRawToken","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensRaw\/documentation\/OUDSTokensRaw\/GridRawToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:13OUDSTokensRaw04GridB5Tokena"}]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensRaw\/documentation\/OUDSTokensRaw\/GridRawTokens\/gridExtraCompactMargin","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://OUDSTokensRaw/documentation/OUDSTokensRaw/GridRawToken":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"GridRawToken"}],"fragments":[{"text":"typealias","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"GridRawToken"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudstokensraw\/gridrawtoken","abstract":[{"text":"In the global design system tool, the notion of “raw tokens of grids” exist but refers always to dimension raw tokens,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to keep grammar clean and clear with design system grammar.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"GridRawToken","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensRaw\/documentation\/OUDSTokensRaw\/GridRawToken"},"doc://OUDSTokensRaw/documentation/OUDSTokensRaw/GridRawTokens":{"fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"GridRawTokens"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensRaw\/documentation\/OUDSTokensRaw\/GridRawTokens","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"GridRawTokens","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Defined as the group of all "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"raw tokens","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" related to "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"grid"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Primitive types such as ","type":"text"},{"code":"Int","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" must be used to as to allow to use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@objc"},{"type":"text","text":" keywords in extensions for overriding."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Such tokens are packed in a ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift enum"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" so as to gather them in one object with the suitable namespace and avoid to have just constants in nothing else","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"(i.e. publicly accessible from everywhere). More optimized than "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"struct","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"GridRawTokens","url":"\/documentation\/oudstokensraw\/gridrawtokens"},"doc://OUDSTokensRaw/documentation/OUDSTokensRaw/GridRawTokens/gridExtraCompactMargin":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudstokensraw\/gridrawtokens\/gridextracompa